cotton.network

Class DummyServiceChain

  • java.lang.Object
    • cotton.network.DummyServiceChain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceChain, java.io.Serializable

    public class DummyServiceChain
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceChain, java.io.Serializable
    The DummyServiceChain implements the ServiceChain interface and maintains the chain of services to be executed.
    See Also:
    ServiceChain, Serialized Form
